<!-- ── Experience ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="experience" id="experience">
  <h2 class="section-heading">Experience</h2>
  <div class="experience-content">

    <div class="row">
      <div class="card year">2026</div>
      <div class="card job">
        <h3 class="job-title">Masters Abroad</h3>
        <p class="job-description">
          After my professional experiences in Costa Rica, I was
          ready for the next level. I packed my life into a suitcase
          and moved across the world to to pursue a Master's degree at one of Spain's top-ranked universities.
          I wrapped up the coursework with honors, earned the highest possible
          grade on my{' '}
          <a
            aria-label="Master's thesis (opens in a new tab)"
            href="https://docta.ucm.es/entities/publication/7087265c-399e-4874-961d-e50a50a53219"
            target="_blank"
            class="cool-link">thesis</a
          >, saw snow for the first time, and had the best
          time of my life.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="card year responsive-year-top">2025</div>
      <div class="card job">
        <h3 class="job-title">Big Tech</h3>
        <p class="job-description">
          Microsoft opened the door to Big Tech, where I worked as a Software
          Engineer on{' '}
          <a
            aria-label="Azure Cosmos DB (opens in a new tab)"
            href="https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/products/cosmos-db"
            target="_blank"
            class="cool-link">Cosmos DB</a
          >, Azure's globally distributed, multi-model database serving millions
          of requests daily. I contributed to the core engine of a system built
          for planetary-scale workloads and five-nines availability.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card year responsive-year-bottom">2025</div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="card double-year">2023<br />2024</div>
      <div class="card job">
        <h3 class="job-title">Startup Hustle</h3>
        <p class="job-description">
          I traded the corporate playbook for the scrappiness and thrill of the
          startup world at{' '}
          <a
            aria-label="Thoropass (opens in a new tab)"
            href="https://thoropass.com/"
            target="_blank"
            class="cool-link">Thoropass</a
          >, an end-to-end compliance automation platform. I shipped features
          used by enterprise customers undergoing SOC 2 and ISO 27001 audits. My role was as
          dynamic as the environment: Frontend, Backend, Product Support, Scrum
          Master, Presenter... I even cooked up a few memes for our LinkedIn!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="card year responsive-year-top">2022</div>
      <div class="card job">
        <h3 class="job-title">E-commerce Newbie</h3>
        <p class="job-description">
          I kicked off my professional journey in the coolest way imaginable:
          snowboards, surfboards, and a whole lot of goats.{' '}
          <a
            aria-label="Backcountry (opens in a new tab)"
            href="https://www.backcountry.com/"
            target="_blank"
            class="cool-link">Backcountry</a
          > brought me on as an enthusiastic new grad. I built and maintained features
          across their e-commerce platform, while learning the craft of professional software engineering.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card year responsive-year-bottom">2022</div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="card year">2021</div>
      <div class="card job">
        <h3 class="job-title">Senior Year</h3>
        <p class="job-description">
          My final year as an undergrad had it all. I was a
          Teaching Assistant for three courses (Programming Fundamentals,
          Databases, and Experimental Design){' '}
          <a
            aria-label="Angry Blocks Game (opens in a new tab)"
            href="https://creacion-videojuegos.github.io/ccf-build/"
            target="_blank"
            class="link">built a game</a
          > in Unity, and classified to the{' '}
          <a
            aria-label="ICPC World Finals (opens in a new tab)"
            href="https://worldfinals.icpc.global/index.html"
            target="_blank"
            class="cool-link">44<sup>th</sup> ICPC World Finals</a
          >, the world championship of competitive programming. My team was self-proclaimed{' '}
          <a
            aria-label="ICPC World Finals video (opens in a new tab)"
            href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IcnLA1CHnL8&t=643s&ab_channel=ICPCNews"
            target="_blank"
            class="link">"Best Meet-the-Team Video"</a
          >.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
